name: Kawakami
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Derived from Japanese wolves descent, Kawakami Inu is destined to be the leader of the inu packs. Kawakami Inu is a community driven cryptocurrency with a goal to become a decentralized meme token ecosystem.

Being a natural leader, we aim to build the most inclusive and serving community in the world with three main values in mind: integrity, visionary, and humility.
